name: The Mountain [GOT] Mini Dude #121
description: Ser Gregor Clegane was a knight of House Clegane, the older brother of Sandor Clegane, and a notoriously fearsome, extremely lethal and much-feared warrior, with a tendency toward extreme and excessive violence. Due to his incredibly massive size, he is called "The Mountain That Rides" or more often simply "The Mountain." After being poisoned in a duel with Oberyn Martell.
